  • Method Details

    • eval

      Vector eval(Vector v1, Vector v2, double m, double h, double t)
      This method is used to solve a function.
      Parameters:
      v1 - position of Boat. (x0 = x, x1 = y, x2 = angle in degrees boat, x3 = angle in degrees sail (relative to boat)
      v2 - velocities (Wind and Boat). (Wind: x0-x1, Boat x2-x3)
      m - mass of Boat.
      h - step size.
      t - time.
